  "title": "Melted Golden Middle Eastern Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A comforting and cultured Middle Eastern dish featuring lamb kidney, air-fried to perfection and served in a glassy-jelly sauce. This dish is a hearty and flavorful meal that is sure to become a favorite.",
