  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the lamb kidney pieces and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add 1 cup of water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 1 1/2 hours.",
    "Use an air fryer to crisp the lamb pieces, if desired.",
    "Serve the lamb and sauce over rice or couscous."
